Ques 1: Create a java based chat server.In order to complete the assignment you need to perform 	following tasks.

Task1: Multiple clients connect to the server.
Task2: Seperate thread to handle each new incomming thread.
Task3: The chat application is scalable to any no of users.
Task4: Whenevr a new client is connected to server every other connected clients can see him/her 	in their terminal.
Task5: Whenever a user send a msg it is shown on each clients terminal in following format.
	<user> msg

Task6: Inform all users when someone leaves the chatroom.

(evry update should me real time update.)


Hint : Synchronization, multithreading.  
